1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,911
<i> ~ Episode 17 ~</i>

2
00:00:04,395 --> 00:00:07,058
Huanbi Jiejie, your outfit is beautiful

3
00:00:07,058 --> 00:00:08,768
Back at the imperial kitchen,

4
00:00:08,768 --> 00:00:10,088
even those eunuchs were staring at you.

5
00:00:10,397 --> 00:00:12,846
My outfit is the same as young mistress Lingrong's

6
00:00:16,051 --> 00:00:18,139
Young mistress loves Jiejie the most

7
00:00:18,139 --> 00:00:20,609
She shares all her good things with Jiejie

8
00:00:23,333 --> 00:00:26,034
Say, do I wear this outfit better

9
00:00:26,034 --> 00:00:27,693
or does Lingrong wear it better?

10
00:00:28,425 --> 00:00:29,578
Before, about the same

11
00:00:29,578 --> 00:00:32,120
But Jiejie's earrings are sublime

12
00:00:32,120 --> 00:00:33,507
Are they gifts from young mistress?

13
00:00:33,757 --> 00:00:36,072
She's born from a poor family

14
00:00:36,072 --> 00:00:38,977
The best cloths would be a waste on her

15
00:00:39,526 --> 00:00:42,001
Let servant pick it for you. Young mistress watch your step.

16
00:00:43,900 --> 00:00:44,970
Young mistress, look!

17
00:00:45,953 --> 00:00:47,275
What's the big deal?

18
00:00:48,127 --> 00:00:51,018
Young mistress, look. The outfit Huanbi is wearing...

19
00:00:51,018 --> 00:00:53,282
Isn't that the one you gave to Precious smile?

20
00:00:56,584 --> 00:00:57,475
Indeed

21
00:00:58,404 --> 00:01:00,232
Precious Smile is quite generous

22
00:01:00,232 --> 00:01:01,740
Such great material...

23
00:01:01,740 --> 00:01:03,675
Young mistress, you couldn't even bear to wear it yourself

24
00:01:03,675 --> 00:01:05,269
leaving two for her.

25
00:01:05,269 --> 00:01:08,328
But she...gives it to servants!

26
00:01:08,870 --> 00:01:09,885
Don't say nonsense!

27
00:01:13,054 --> 00:01:14,554
Huanbi is Jiejie's close servant from back home

28
00:01:14,554 --> 00:01:18,400
She normally does dress better than others

29
00:01:19,192 --> 00:01:20,690
It's fine if she doesn't want to wear it

30
00:01:20,690 --> 00:01:23,943
but Huanbi is only a servant.

31
00:01:23,943 --> 00:01:27,026
Giving it to her...then what does she think of you?

32
00:01:43,141 --> 00:01:44,219
It smells so fragrant

33
00:01:44,853 --> 00:01:45,978
What took you so long?

34
00:01:46,991 --> 00:01:48,608
It was easy to get the chestnut cake

35
00:01:48,608 --> 00:01:50,988
but I saw that the imperial kitchen had some yuca powder

36
00:01:50,988 --> 00:01:52,378
so I also brought some back.

37
00:01:52,378 --> 00:01:54,760
I thought I'd make some pearl balls tonight

38
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:55,847
as a late-night snack for young mistress.

39
00:01:56,189 --> 00:01:57,311
You're thoughtful

40
00:02:02,476 --> 00:02:04,678
Since favoring Lingering An,

41
00:02:04,678 --> 00:02:06,839
His Majesty has also relaxed a bit.

42
00:02:07,473 --> 00:02:08,980
Before, he would spend 6-7 hours at a time

43
00:02:08,980 --> 00:02:10,510
reading documents

44
00:02:10,510 --> 00:02:12,335
without taking a break.

45
00:02:13,232 --> 00:02:14,859
Listening to songs relaxes him

46
00:02:14,859 --> 00:02:16,000
He should

47
00:02:16,252 --> 00:02:19,591
You are sensible, unlike that moody Princess of Glory

48
00:02:21,713 --> 00:02:22,764
Come

49
00:02:24,285 --> 00:02:26,016
Don't be afraid. It's just a cat.

50
00:02:28,362 --> 00:02:30,152
I heard Persia gave a cat as gift

51
00:02:30,152 --> 00:02:32,361
which the emperor gave to 3rd prince.

52
00:02:32,521 --> 00:02:33,638
This is the one

53
00:02:34,317 --> 00:02:35,598
3rd prince is filial

54
00:02:35,598 --> 00:02:37,274
He knows that Princess of Regularity likes cats

55
00:02:37,274 --> 00:02:38,753
so he gave it to her.

56
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:40,639
But when Princess of Regularity brought it over the other day,

57
00:02:43,082 --> 00:02:45,478
So she gave it to me

58
00:02:46,374 --> 00:02:48,751
I gave it a name, Pine nut

59
00:02:49,808 --> 00:02:50,776
Pretty name

60
00:02:51,589 --> 00:02:52,894
You hold it?

61
00:02:54,947 --> 00:02:56,880
I forgot. You're afraid of cats.

62
00:02:58,344 --> 00:02:59,751
Empress shows care for me

63
00:02:59,751 --> 00:03:01,730
You need not remember these little things

64
00:03:03,438 --> 00:03:04,553
Come, sit

65
00:03:08,697 --> 00:03:10,575
Actually, although I really like it,

66
00:03:10,575 --> 00:03:12,558
I must be careful.

67
00:03:13,497 --> 00:03:14,856
It is an animal after all

68
00:03:14,856 --> 00:03:17,806
If I'm not careful and get bitten or scratched,

69
00:03:17,806 --> 00:03:18,789
that would not be good.

70
00:03:18,789 --> 00:03:20,061
Empress worries too much

71
00:03:20,061 --> 00:03:22,482
Pine nut was raised by you

72
00:03:22,482 --> 00:03:23,936
It's very docile

73
00:03:24,255 --> 00:03:25,247
Really?

74
00:03:25,816 --> 00:03:28,246
Even people are unpredictable, much less animals

75
00:03:31,159 --> 00:03:34,632
It's easy to let your guard down around those who are docile and close

76
00:03:39,546 --> 00:03:40,746
Today's the 7th

77
00:03:40,746 --> 00:03:43,058
His Majesty invited all the dukes and inner palace

78
00:03:43,058 --> 00:03:45,037
to enjoy the full moon at Chang Chun garden tonight.

79
00:03:45,488 --> 00:03:46,623
Don't be late

80
00:03:47,624 --> 00:03:48,521
Yes

81
00:03:51,022 --> 00:03:52,376
Tonight's the 7th

82
00:03:52,376 --> 00:03:54,938
I wish Your Majesties everlasting love,

83
00:03:54,938 --> 00:03:56,349
fortune, and longevity.

84
00:04:12,406 --> 00:04:15,510
We sisters forgot

85
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:19,413
It's a shame

86
00:04:21,073 --> 00:04:23,450
I see that the grapes on your table are a tribute

87
00:04:23,954 --> 00:04:25,366
Give them to me

88
00:04:26,711 --> 00:04:27,571
Yes

89
00:04:30,921 --> 00:04:32,682
Your Majesty, you have some yourself

90
00:04:32,682 --> 00:04:34,830
What do you want mine?

91
00:04:35,055 --> 00:04:36,522
I see that you're busy talking,

92
00:04:36,522 --> 00:04:38,162
not eating,

93
00:04:38,162 --> 00:04:40,954
so you might as well give them to me and not waste them.

94
00:04:45,305 --> 00:04:48,724
Your Majesty likes to joke with me

95
00:04:51,129 --> 00:04:52,561
Lately, His Majesty

96
00:04:52,561 --> 00:04:54,281
only likes to joke with Lingering An.

97
00:04:57,067 --> 00:04:58,851
To others,

98
00:04:58,851 --> 00:05:01,609
it sounds like you're trying to steal her thunder.

99
00:05:07,270 --> 00:05:08,629
I have little talent and even less learning

100
00:05:08,629 --> 00:05:11,082
Niang Niang please advise me in more matters

101
00:05:11,082 --> 00:05:13,060
I would like to toast Princess of Glory

102
00:05:28,432 --> 00:05:30,502
Princess of Glory is magnanimous

103
00:05:43,206 --> 00:05:44,896
I'm a bit drunk. I want to take a walk outside.

104
00:05:46,189 --> 00:05:48,860
This is my first time here. I'm not familiar with the garden.

105
00:05:48,860 --> 00:05:51,435
How about Auntie Jin Xi go with young mistress?

106
00:05:55,627 --> 00:05:57,871
Your Majesty, I toast you

107
00:06:08,077 --> 00:06:09,476
It feels so confined here

108
00:06:11,254 --> 00:06:12,325
This Chang Chun garden

109
00:06:12,325 --> 00:06:15,082
used to be the late emperor Kang Xi's favorite temporary residence.

110
00:06:16,065 --> 00:06:18,465
After he passed away, it became more deserted.

111
00:06:20,812 --> 00:06:23,470
Look, just ahead is Tonghua Terrace

112
00:06:24,710 --> 00:06:26,373
Young mistress wants to walk around outside

113
00:06:26,373 --> 00:06:29,596
It's too noisy near the banquet

114
00:06:29,596 --> 00:06:31,302
Let's go look inside

115
00:06:32,158 --> 00:06:33,425
Tonghua Terrace?

116
00:06:34,911 --> 00:06:37,210
Such a unique, elegant name is rare in the palace

117
00:06:37,954 --> 00:06:39,028
I heard that

118
00:06:39,028 --> 00:06:42,259
that the Chinese parasol tree is the most loving, virtuous tree

119
00:06:43,269 --> 00:06:46,975
so the late emperor dedicated this place to Princess Shu.

120
00:06:48,802 --> 00:06:50,218
But it's a pity, that Princess Shu

121
00:06:50,218 --> 00:06:54,494
During the late emperor's rule she was highly favored

122
00:06:54,994 --> 00:06:59,666
But now she's a nun. It's really sad.

123
00:07:02,450 --> 00:07:03,770
Why is it so deserted?

124
00:07:05,293 --> 00:07:06,294
After His Majesty took the throne,

125
00:07:06,294 --> 00:07:08,574
Empress Dowager thought Tonghua Terrace was too worn down.

126
00:07:08,574 --> 00:07:11,587
People rarely come here

127
00:07:11,587 --> 00:07:13,244
so it gradually became deserted.

128
00:07:15,223 --> 00:07:16,498
No matter how beautiful the love and things were

129
00:07:16,852 --> 00:07:18,596
they just lasted for only a short time

130
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:20,694
Tonghua Terrace is such an example

131
00:07:21,451 --> 00:07:24,172
so was the love between the late emperor and Princess of Su

132
00:07:25,105 --> 00:07:25,974
Yes

133
00:07:28,352 --> 00:07:30,004
You stay here. I will go take a look.

134
00:07:33,634 --> 00:07:35,051
Be careful!

135
00:07:43,858 --> 00:07:45,780
Tonghua Terrace

136
00:08:01,014 --> 00:08:02,551
Do you know what flower that is?

137
00:08:02,551 --> 00:08:03,330
Who?!

138
00:08:03,846 --> 00:08:05,883
Why does Precious Smile ask "who"

139
00:08:05,883 --> 00:08:07,488
everytime you see me?

140
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:09,956
Seems that my appearance

141
00:08:09,956 --> 00:08:12,381
is indeed not very memorable.

142
00:08:12,888 --> 00:08:14,747
Duke loves to sneak up behind people

143
00:08:14,747 --> 00:08:16,893
Of course it's alarming

144
00:08:17,385 --> 00:08:19,086
It's Precious Smile who walked up before me

145
00:08:19,086 --> 00:08:20,869
and didn't see me.

146
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:23,620
It is not I who likes to hide behind you

147
00:08:24,384 --> 00:08:26,823
Tonghua Terrace is full of plants. I failed to see you.

148
00:08:26,823 --> 00:08:29,652
But why didn't Duke say something earlier?

149
00:08:32,142 --> 00:08:34,294
I thought you looked worried today

150
00:08:34,294 --> 00:08:35,648
unlike in the past

151
00:08:36,252 --> 00:08:37,959
so I dared not alarm you.

152
00:08:38,838 --> 00:08:40,895
But I still ended up frightening Precious Smile

153
00:08:41,663 --> 00:08:42,874
That was not my intention

154
00:08:44,331 --> 00:08:47,017
I'm just a bit drunk. Thanks for Duke's concern.

155
00:08:48,129 --> 00:08:49,373
There is a celebratory banquet in the palace

156
00:08:49,373 --> 00:08:51,584
Why is Precious Smile out here?

157
00:08:52,980 --> 00:08:54,153
Tonight is the July 7th (Chinese valentine's day)

158
00:08:54,153 --> 00:08:56,357
the moon light is more attracting

159
00:08:57,551 --> 00:08:59,189
Exactly

160
00:09:00,913 --> 00:09:02,846
(Poem about July 7th) When autumn’s Golden Wind embraces Dew of Jade

161
00:09:02,846 --> 00:09:05,565
All the love scenes on earth, however many, fade

162
00:09:06,492 --> 00:09:09,598
If we just drink during such a beautiful night

163
00:09:10,123 --> 00:09:11,297
What a waste

164
00:09:12,659 --> 00:09:13,778
Just as you said

165
00:09:13,778 --> 00:09:16,331
I was literary pursuits by a fluke for once

166
00:09:17,987 --> 00:09:21,151
Precious Smile seems to really like the flowers on the terrace

167
00:09:22,507 --> 00:09:23,351
Indeed

168
00:09:23,351 --> 00:09:25,921
When I was young, I often saw them outside in the fields

169
00:09:25,921 --> 00:09:27,334
They're called morning glory

170
00:09:27,727 --> 00:09:30,189
I rarely see this flower in the palace

171
00:09:30,189 --> 00:09:31,976
so they are even more unique.

172
00:09:32,646 --> 00:09:36,038
This flower has another name - sunset

173
00:09:37,057 --> 00:09:38,574
Indeed it shouldn't be in the palace

174
00:09:39,092 --> 00:09:42,416
The palace does not plant flowers with such a short lifespan

175
00:09:43,562 --> 00:09:44,780
Flowers also have short lifespans?

176
00:09:44,780 --> 00:09:47,612
I thought only women did

177
00:09:48,827 --> 00:09:52,742
They say this flower is lowly, just bloom in the corner

178
00:09:52,742 --> 00:09:54,937
blooms at dusk, and falls in the next morning

179
00:09:54,937 --> 00:09:58,423
no one enjoy it, so the saying goes

180
00:09:58,838 --> 00:10:00,023
So it is called short lifespan?

181
00:10:01,407 --> 00:10:03,244
But I think this flower is extraordinary

182
00:10:04,146 --> 00:10:05,176
sunset

183
00:10:06,018 --> 00:10:08,392
it is the beautiful sunset scenery

184
00:10:10,831 --> 00:10:12,194
Do you think so

185
00:10:13,339 --> 00:10:15,240
I just don't want to regard such a pure and beautiful flower

186
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:17,316
as short lifespan

187
00:10:24,528 --> 00:10:25,680
Where is Precious Smile

188
00:10:27,332 --> 00:10:28,554
Your majesty

189
00:10:28,554 --> 00:10:31,165
young mistress was drunk, so she went to the side hall to change clothes

190
00:10:33,278 --> 00:10:34,924
Smile Jiejie is usually weak-headed

191
00:10:34,924 --> 00:10:36,431
can't compare with your majesty's great capacity for liquor

192
00:10:40,313 --> 00:10:41,757
The imperial family's night

193
00:10:41,757 --> 00:10:44,875
Precious and I come here to avoid the noisy world

194
00:10:45,667 --> 00:10:46,980
it is not proper

195
00:10:47,729 --> 00:10:49,010
I'm nearsightedness

196
00:10:49,527 --> 00:10:51,574
I can only see the sunset

197
00:10:52,426 --> 00:10:55,373
I heared that Lingering An

198
00:10:55,373 --> 00:10:57,254
is introduced to his majesty by you

199
00:10:58,830 --> 00:11:00,846
are you feeling sorrow because of her?

200
00:11:03,199 --> 00:11:04,828
We are sisters in the palaces

201
00:11:06,018 --> 00:11:07,398
you are joking

202
00:11:07,969 --> 00:11:09,786
Actually it's a good thing to have someone share the favor

203
00:11:10,787 --> 00:11:13,072
If Precious Smile monopolizes all the favor

204
00:11:13,072 --> 00:11:15,467
and becomes the object of hatred in the six palaces,

205
00:11:15,467 --> 00:11:18,417
I would really cry for you.

206
00:11:19,799 --> 00:11:20,586
Many thanks Duke

207
00:11:21,341 --> 00:11:22,523
Precious is exceptionally intelligent

208
00:11:22,523 --> 00:11:24,266
My words are superfluous

209
00:11:24,862 --> 00:11:26,236
But as a bystander,

210
00:11:26,236 --> 00:11:28,987
I find that you seem to have walked into a puzzle.

211
00:11:28,987 --> 00:11:31,497
So I wanted to say something

212
00:11:32,356 --> 00:11:34,933
It's very kind of you to advise me

213
00:11:35,843 --> 00:11:37,404
Imperial brother is the ruler of the country

214
00:11:37,404 --> 00:11:39,656
On some things, he has no choice

215
00:11:39,656 --> 00:11:42,626
I hope Precious will understand him

216
00:11:44,535 --> 00:11:46,063
I'm actually very glad

217
00:11:46,063 --> 00:11:47,681
to not be the emperor.

218
00:11:48,374 --> 00:11:52,291
I need not be bothered by all these worries

219
00:11:54,863 --> 00:11:56,734
Duke's name is known everywhere

220
00:11:56,734 --> 00:11:59,877
I'm afraid you're the prince charming many girls dream about

221
00:12:03,675 --> 00:12:04,983
I dare not be greedy

222
00:12:04,983 --> 00:12:07,553
I only wish for one soulmate to spend my life with

223
00:12:08,044 --> 00:12:10,528
don't want many beautiful concubines.

224
00:12:11,965 --> 00:12:13,060
Easy said

225
00:12:15,811 --> 00:12:17,103
Precious doesn't believe me?

226
00:12:17,932 --> 00:12:19,057
I personally think that

227
00:12:19,057 --> 00:12:20,769
to truly love someone

228
00:12:20,769 --> 00:12:22,899
is to cherish each other

229
00:12:22,899 --> 00:12:26,656
and not hurt each other in any way.

230
00:12:29,796 --> 00:12:31,611
If Duke's words are true,

231
00:12:31,611 --> 00:12:34,252
then the future 17th Fu'jin is very fortunate.

232
00:12:36,219 --> 00:12:38,775
your suggestion is very commendable

233
00:12:39,314 --> 00:12:40,291
Precious need not thank me

234
00:12:40,996 --> 00:12:43,724
I just don't wish imperial brother to favor Precious too much

235
00:12:45,293 --> 00:12:48,007
causing Precious to follow in my mother's footsteps.

236
00:12:48,007 --> 00:12:51,445
only the candles and Buddha accompany her

237
00:12:55,482 --> 00:12:57,728
It is rare for emperors to have true love

238
00:12:58,828 --> 00:12:59,728
if they do

239
00:12:59,728 --> 00:13:01,577
they will hide it in the dark

240
00:13:01,577 --> 00:13:03,244
and others also can't accept it

241
00:13:04,558 --> 00:13:08,706
Just like sunset, only blooms for one night

242
00:13:12,126 --> 00:13:14,577
I've been out here too long, I must leave now

243
00:13:14,994 --> 00:13:16,370
When I abruptly showed up last time,

244
00:13:16,370 --> 00:13:17,992
it was not my intention.

245
00:13:19,447 --> 00:13:20,841
The day of Princess Wenyi's birthday,

246
00:13:20,841 --> 00:13:23,254
was also the day Mother entered the palace many years ago.

247
00:13:24,333 --> 00:13:27,027
I was thinking of the past, and couldn't restrain myself in the moment

248
00:13:27,721 --> 00:13:28,565
I lost my manners

249
00:13:29,977 --> 00:13:31,725
I don't know what Duke is referring to

250
00:13:31,725 --> 00:13:33,214
I don't even remember

251
00:13:38,629 --> 00:13:41,818
Yes...I don't remember either...

252
00:13:42,115 --> 00:13:43,257
Goodbye

253
00:14:09,187 --> 00:14:10,743
What took you so long outside?

254
00:14:13,908 --> 00:14:16,313
I don't have much alcohol tolerance. I went outside to get some fresh air.

255
00:14:17,376 --> 00:14:20,009
I saw a type of flower called "sunset"

256
00:14:20,961 --> 00:14:22,168
I was mesmerized

257
00:14:22,314 --> 00:14:24,853
Sunset? What kind of flower is that?

258
00:14:26,391 --> 00:14:28,901
I saw that the crape myrtles in the courtyard were blossoming well

259
00:14:28,901 --> 00:14:31,869
I will order someone to bring you several pots

260
00:14:33,971 --> 00:14:37,091
Now is the season for crape myrtles to bloom

261
00:14:37,553 --> 00:14:38,629
Many thanks Your Majesty

262
00:14:40,997 --> 00:14:43,232
Your Majesty is so good to Sister Smile

263
00:14:43,811 --> 00:14:45,502
His Majesty treats everyone in the six palaces equally

264
00:14:45,502 --> 00:14:47,012
He's also very good to Jiejie

265
00:14:47,446 --> 00:14:48,534
Yes

266
00:14:49,504 --> 00:14:51,192
Your majesty give each of us equal favor

267
00:14:51,192 --> 00:14:54,038
Empress and all the concubines in the harem

268
00:14:54,038 --> 00:14:55,467
are nourished by your favor

269
00:14:56,495 --> 00:14:59,489
I'll drink a toast

270
00:15:17,473 --> 00:15:21,160
Your Majesty, I have something to take care of. I would like to pardon myself.

271
00:15:21,160 --> 00:15:22,543
What's so urgent?

272
00:15:23,494 --> 00:15:26,397
