00:31:52,858 --> 00:31:54,717
I saw something big happening inside

543
00:31:54,717 --> 00:31:57,079
so I dared not come in right away.

544
00:32:01,465 --> 00:32:03,215
But it's a good thing I came

545
00:32:04,174 --> 00:32:07,810
Otherwise someone would be unjustly accused

546
00:32:10,101 --> 00:32:13,862
Princess of Modesty, you say you were with Precious Smile that night

547
00:32:13,862 --> 00:32:15,614
Is that true?

548
00:32:17,582 --> 00:32:20,661
That night, I thought Precious Smile seemed a bit drunk

549
00:32:20,661 --> 00:32:24,846
and was worried so I went to check on her with Jixiang.

550
00:32:25,774 --> 00:32:29,834
Afterwards, we both went back to my palace

551
00:32:30,687 --> 00:32:31,906
and chatted for a long time.

552
00:32:32,526 --> 00:32:33,492
Jixiang

553
00:32:33,861 --> 00:32:34,481
Yes

554
00:32:36,597 --> 00:32:39,577
That night, Niang Niang and Precious Smile discussed Buddhist scriptures

555
00:32:39,577 --> 00:32:40,716
They really hit it off

556
00:32:40,716 --> 00:32:42,884
Then Precious Smile said it was getting late

557
00:32:42,884 --> 00:32:44,110
and hurried back.

558
00:32:45,580 --> 00:32:46,806
That means

559
00:32:46,806 --> 00:32:48,320
Princess Wenyi's incident

560
00:32:48,320 --> 00:32:50,199
has nothing to do with Precious Smile?

561
00:32:51,906 --> 00:32:54,746
Princess of Modesty came just in the nick of time, like a much needed rain

562
00:32:55,622 --> 00:32:58,246
Princess of Modesty has always stayed in her palace nursing her health, never leaving home

563
00:32:58,246 --> 00:33:02,265
That night, why did you ignore the imperial doctors' advice

564
00:33:02,265 --> 00:33:03,989
and go out at night?

565
00:33:05,705 --> 00:33:08,141
Indeed, bedridden people should not go out

566
00:33:09,058 --> 00:33:10,722
But on the day of the banquet,

567
00:33:10,722 --> 00:33:14,456
I heard excellent music

568
00:33:14,456 --> 00:33:17,257
and went outside as if in a rapture.

569
00:33:18,402 --> 00:33:21,639
I wasn't expecting the good luck of meeting Precious Smile

570
00:33:22,189 --> 00:33:24,676
Yes, I feel the same way

571
00:33:26,135 --> 00:33:28,817
Oh? Then why didn't Precious Smile

572
00:33:28,817 --> 00:33:32,398
mention meeting Princess of Modesty earlier?

573
00:33:40,318 --> 00:33:41,742
I shouldn't have hidden this

574
00:33:42,463 --> 00:33:43,995
When Princess of Modesty went out that day,

575
00:33:43,995 --> 00:33:45,804
she didn't want anyone to know

576
00:33:45,804 --> 00:33:47,803
to avoid worrying the Emperor and Empress.

577
00:33:47,803 --> 00:33:50,728
So about our meeting that day

578
00:33:50,728 --> 00:33:53,216
I didn't want to tell anyone.

579
00:33:53,216 --> 00:33:56,252
Who knew this would involve the princess?

580
00:33:56,252 --> 00:34:00,889
I know that the Emperor is wise, the Empress intelligent,

581
00:34:00,889 --> 00:34:02,887
and will definitely uphold my innocence.

582
00:34:02,887 --> 00:34:05,711
I didn't want to lose Princess of Modesty's trust,

583
00:34:05,711 --> 00:34:07,888
so I kept my lips sealed.

584
00:34:09,085 --> 00:34:12,023
What, Princess of Glory doesn't believe it?

585
00:34:12,810 --> 00:34:13,960
I am not being mistrustful

586
00:34:14,985 --> 00:34:16,211
I just think that

587
00:34:16,211 --> 00:34:19,928
Princess of Modesty seems very partial to Precious Smile.

588
00:34:22,461 --> 00:34:25,298
I've only met Precious Smile twice

589
00:34:26,191 --> 00:34:29,556
The first time was also at Wenyi's birthday banquet

590
00:34:37,795 --> 00:34:39,217
Why would I lie

591
00:34:39,217 --> 00:34:41,289
to protect someone I don't know very well?

592
00:34:51,346 --> 00:34:52,302
Get up

593
00:34:56,481 --> 00:34:57,604
Sit

594
00:34:57,604 --> 00:34:59,327
Have the imperial doctor take a good look later

595
00:35:00,366 --> 00:35:01,620
Summer clothes are thin

596
00:35:01,620 --> 00:35:03,361
Don't hurt yourself from kneeling

597
00:35:04,479 --> 00:35:06,766
Precious Smile keeps her promises

598
00:35:15,935 --> 00:35:19,232
It's reasonable for Princess of Glory to not believe me

599
00:35:19,973 --> 00:35:21,674
When I was just outside the room,

600
00:35:21,674 --> 00:35:23,567
I thought I heard the servant ladies say

601
00:35:23,567 --> 00:35:25,512
that they saw Precious Smile

602
00:35:25,512 --> 00:35:27,244
walking in the direction of Cool and Refreshing Hall that night.

603
00:35:27,883 --> 00:35:30,282
Might as well make things clear now

604
00:35:31,429 --> 00:35:34,397
to end the dispute once and for all.

605
00:35:37,020 --> 00:35:38,263
Say again

606
00:35:39,174 --> 00:35:40,966
Did you see, with your own yes, Precious Smile enter

607
00:35:40,966 --> 00:35:42,519
the Cool and Refreshing Hall?

608
00:35:43,225 --> 00:35:44,797
Servant did see Precious Smile

609
00:35:44,797 --> 00:35:46,143
walk in the direction of Cool and Refreshing Hall.

610
00:35:46,143 --> 00:35:49,745
As for whether she went inside, it seemed...

611
00:35:49,745 --> 00:35:52,532
What seemed?! That's totally groundless!

612
00:35:53,844 --> 00:35:54,494
What about you?

613
00:35:54,721 --> 00:35:55,651
Servant...

614
00:35:55,651 --> 00:35:58,081
Servant only saw Precious Smile walking with Auntie Jinxi

615
00:36:00,378 --> 00:36:02,107
Your Majesty, what do you think?

616
00:36:02,245 --> 00:36:03,139
Do as you see fit!

617
00:36:03,775 --> 00:36:04,799
Just one thing

618
00:36:04,799 --> 00:36:07,170
Don't go easy on this bad habit of chasing wind and clutching at shadows (making groundless accusations)!

619
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:08,790
Yes

620
00:36:13,922 --> 00:36:17,225
Drag them out and give 80 face slaps each! As a warning to others!

621
00:36:20,355 --> 00:36:22,125
Precious Smile, please wait

622
00:36:41,382 --> 00:36:44,783
Is Precious Smile willing to walk with me?

623
00:36:48,871 --> 00:36:50,214
I was just thinking the same

624
00:36:53,872 --> 00:36:56,978
Many thanks Niang Niang for helping me today

625
00:36:57,682 --> 00:37:00,976
I have my reasons for helping you

626
00:37:05,515 --> 00:37:07,152
Niang Niang really believes I'm innocent?

627
00:37:08,571 --> 00:37:09,588
That day,

628
00:37:09,588 --> 00:37:12,542
I saw you walk out of Chang Chun Garden with a servant

629
00:37:12,542 --> 00:37:14,341
and pass by my palace.

630
00:37:15,154 --> 00:37:18,058
By calculating the time, I knew it wasn't you

631
00:37:18,831 --> 00:37:21,274
I was in a hurry that day and didn't see Niang Niang

632
00:37:21,864 --> 00:37:22,926
I hope Niang Niang will forgive me

633
00:37:25,142 --> 00:37:26,446
These are all little things

634
00:37:27,336 --> 00:37:28,904
Princess Wenyi is very cute

635
00:37:28,904 --> 00:37:32,728
but she's suffering so much torment at such a young age.

636
00:37:34,330 --> 00:37:35,524
Although Princess's body is weak,

637
00:37:35,524 --> 00:37:39,207
she is the emperor's daughter and protected by the gods.

638
00:37:43,203 --> 00:37:44,786
Precious Cao's child

639
00:37:44,786 --> 00:37:47,277
originally couldn't be born.

640
00:37:47,277 --> 00:37:49,554
She became pregnant at the wrong time

641
00:37:49,554 --> 00:37:53,509
It was also a difficult birth. The fetal position was not right.

642
00:37:54,976 --> 00:37:56,832
It nearly cost her life

643
00:37:57,922 --> 00:38:01,411
But the emperor especially loves and dotes on this child

644
00:38:02,922 --> 00:38:06,189
Children in this palace seem great

645
00:38:07,011 --> 00:38:08,377
but they suffer way more ailments and disasters

646
00:38:08,377 --> 00:38:11,743
than children outside.

647
00:38:15,787 --> 00:38:18,248
Precious Smile, you were the target in all this

648
00:38:19,169 --> 00:38:21,322
You must take good care of yourself

649
00:38:22,373 --> 00:38:24,576
I can protect you once today

650
00:38:24,576 --> 00:38:27,256
but not all the time.

651
00:38:29,093 --> 00:38:30,424
Thanks Niang Niang for being thoroughly considerate

652
00:38:31,488 --> 00:38:35,324
I will visit Niang Niang when I have time

653
00:38:35,928 --> 00:38:36,922
No need

654
00:38:45,760 --> 00:38:50,661
Besides, it would be more beneficial

655
00:38:50,661 --> 00:38:52,855
if we don't see each other that much.

656
00:38:53,881 --> 00:38:55,045
Yes

657
00:38:58,287 --> 00:38:59,507
Precious Smile,

658
00:38:59,507 --> 00:39:02,072
Niang Niang's body is weak and should go back early to rest.

659
00:39:02,348 --> 00:39:04,522
Then I won't disturb you anymore

660
00:39:18,413 --> 00:39:19,155
Niang Niang

661
00:39:22,623 --> 00:39:24,158
How should this matter be handled?

662
00:39:25,182 --> 00:39:27,597
Yes, I've already thought about it

663
00:39:27,597 --> 00:39:30,003
How about letting some one be the scapegoat

664
00:39:30,003 --> 00:39:31,149
and end this

665
00:39:32,237 --> 00:39:33,781
Do you guarantee no problems?

666
00:39:34,055 --> 00:39:35,319
Yes, I'm willing to guarantee

667
00:39:37,305 --> 00:39:40,719
That's good. As long as I'm not exposed.

668
00:39:43,174 --> 00:39:44,663
Crying all day and night, so annoying

669
00:39:44,663 --> 00:39:46,442
Take her away!

670
00:39:47,582 --> 00:39:48,495
Yes!

671
00:39:49,303 --> 00:39:50,846
Then bring her back later

672
00:39:52,608 --> 00:39:53,817
I understand

